{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/blog/2024-07-25-how-to-add-max-length-in-react-js/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends 👋, Welcome To aHoisting! To add max length in react js, you can use . It will add max length in react js. Today, I am going to show you, how to add…","html":"<p>Hi Friends 👋,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aHoisting!</p>\n<p>To add max length in react js, you can use <code class=\"language-text\">maxLength={10}</code>. It will add max length in react js.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to add max length in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install and create a new React app.</li>\n<li>Import react component.</li>\n<li>Create a Component.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let’s start with the first step.</p>\n<h2>Step 1: Install and create a new React app.</h2>\n<p>First you have to install the React project. You should use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> command to create a new React project.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">npx create<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\ncd my<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>app\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 2: Import react component.</h2>\n<p>After installing, you have to import your React component. To do this, add the following <code class=\"language-text\">./MaxLengthInput'</code> to the top of your component file.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> MaxLengthInput <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./MaxLengthInput'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Step 3: Create a Component.</h2>\n<p>You can use <code class=\"language-text\">maxLength={10}</code> to add max length in react js.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>input\n        type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text\"</span>\n        value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>inputValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        onChange<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        maxLength<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Set the maximum length to 10 characters</span>\n        placeholder<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Type here...\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>inputValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* Show the character count */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Add max length example.</h2>\n<p>The below code is an example of a React. You have to import <code class=\"language-text\">./MaxLengthInput</code> and set <code class=\"language-text\">maxLength={10}</code> to add max length in react js.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> MaxLengthInput <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./MaxLengthInput'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"App\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>MaxLengthInput <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">MaxLengthInput.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> useState <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">MaxLengthInput</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>inputValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setInputValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">useState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">handleChange</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">setInputValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>input\n        type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"text\"</span>\n        value<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>inputValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        onChange<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>handleChange<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        maxLength<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Set the maximum length to 10 characters</span>\n        placeholder<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Type here...\"</span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>inputValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* Show the character count */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> MaxLengthInput<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above code example, I have used the <code class=\"language-text\">maxLength={10}</code> to add max length in react js.</p>\n<p>Check the output of the above code.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 361px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bf554097a0abe0d894c211c9b8eab47f/c316d/max-length.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 69.62025316455697%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRlAAAABXRUJQVlA4IEQAAABwAwCdASoUAA4APtFYpEwoJSOiMAgBABoJQBOj+ABgaLZzd9AA/VP4Z81HSVYKYQx9HT4Yj/hf5bi+1G4eJHrjhFAAAA=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, add, max, length\"\n        title=\"React, add, max, length\"\n        src=\"/static/bf554097a0abe0d894c211c9b8eab47f/c316d/max-length.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bf554097a0abe0d894c211c9b8eab47f/81b7c/max-length.webp 158w,\n/static/bf554097a0abe0d894c211c9b8eab47f/6ea66/max-length.webp 315w,\n/static/bf554097a0abe0d894c211c9b8eab47f/c316d/max-length.webp 361w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 361px) 100vw, 361px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>All the best 👍</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to add max length in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"July 25, 2024","description":"Example of add max length in react js with step by step tutorial - aHoisting","social_image":{"absolutePath":"/Users/mac/Documents/hoisting/ahoisting/static/media/template/reactjs.jpg"}}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":